snippet.textDisplay: On this occasion of Eid, I bow down to Coke Studio for making another immortal rendition in Raga Bhairavi. The contours, the chalan, the taan, everything is just as beautiful as it is in any immortal thumri. The style shifts from Bashir sahab to Ali sahab are magnificent. This shift is the switch from thumri to qawwali and back again. This is not only rare, but practically unseen. Couldn't have asked for a better gift for Bhairavi from you people. This, shall live, if not in everyone's hearts, in my heart for ever.
